<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8230820>
    dc:description "Figures 5–13. Details ofAnomocephalobus liuhaoi gen. et sp. nov., holotype,NIGP177044, under confocal microscopy: (5) mouthparts,ventral view;(6) antenna,dorsal view; (7) compound eye,dorsal view;(8) compound eye,ventral view;(9) crenulate posterior pronotal margin (arrowhead), dorsal view; (10) pronotal hypomeron, ventral view; (11) mesothorax,ventral view;(12) metacoxa, ventral view; (13) ovipositor, ventral view. (an1–11) antennomeres 1–11, (cl) clypeus, (el) elytron, (ey) compound eye, (hy) hypomeron, (lb) labrum, (msv) mesoventrite, (mtc) metacoxa, (mttc) metatrochanter, (mtv) metaventrite, (ov) ovipositor, (pn) pronotum, (ps) prosternum, (v5) ventrite 5. Scale bars: 200 Μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8230820/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

